description.narrative: UNICEF provided support to enhance the capacities of national stakeholders as required by the Code on the Rights of the Child. UNICEF continued to enhance the educational system to adopt new teaching practices and technologies, enhance teachers’ capacity, meet the needs of out-of-school children;and prevent violence. At the same time, UNICEF also provided support for enhancing the capacity of the child protection and educational systems to respond to COVID-19 challenges and directly reached out to the most vulnerable children and families. | Status:Met | As-of Date:15/01/2021
